# {{TITLE}} Adapter

**Status**: STUB · scaffolded {{DATE}} · TODO: implement + fill investigation-reference.md.

## Declared INPUTS

- Asset path (from invoker prompt).
- Sibling `asset.yaml` `deployment:` block: `platform`, `publish_method`, `location`,
  `format_requirements`, `verification`, `deployment_notes` (per `docs/specs/asset.md`).
- Tenant `integrations.yaml#platforms.{{NAME}}`: `has_adapter`, `credentials` (env-var refs),
  `defaults` (per `docs/specs/integrations.md`).

## Declared OUTPUTS — the adapter envelope

Returns JSON to CM (see ADAPTER-CONTRACT.md § adapter envelope):

```json
{
  "status": "deployed | dry_run | aborted | failed",
  "platform": "{{NAME}}",
  "target": "<where it went / would go>",
  "verification": { "automated": [...], "manual": [...] },
  "operator_action": "<the one next thing, or ''>",
  "notes": "<deployment_notes + adapter remarks>"
}
```

